<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="EXIT Realty privacy policy, including data collection, cookie usage, payment processing, and your privacy rights."
  lastUpdated="March 28, 2025"
  source={{ label: 'EXIT Realty Central privacy policy', url: 'https://www.exitrealtycentral.com/privacy' }}
>
  <p>
      EXIT Realty Corp. International and its subsidiaries (collectively, “ERCI,” “we,” “us,” or
      “our”) respect your privacy and are committed to safeguarding your Personal Information. This
      Privacy Policy describes how Personal Information is collected, used, disclosed, retained, and
      protected in connection with our services.
  </p>

  <h2>Scope</h2>
  <p>
      This policy applies to visitors and users who interact with EXIT Realty websites, services, and
      related platforms, including this site.
  </p>

  <h2>Information Collected</h2>
  <ul>
      <li>Information you submit through forms (name, email, phone, and message details).</li>
      <li>Transaction details when services are purchased (processed by third-party providers).</li>
      <li>Automatically collected usage data (IP address, browser, operating system, and timestamps).</li>
      <li>Cookie and tracking data used for analytics, functionality, and security.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How Information Is Used</h2>
  <ul>
      <li>To provide and improve services and respond to inquiries.</li>
      <li>To process transactions and communicate service updates.</li>
      <li>To analyze performance, improve user experience, and prevent fraud.</li>
      <li>To meet legal and regulatory obligations.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Payment Processing</h2>
  <p>
      Payments may be processed by Stripe. Stripe handles payment information in accordance with its own
      privacy policy and security controls.
  </p>

  <h2>Sharing and Transfers</h2>
  <p>
      Personal Information may be shared with service providers, legal authorities when required, and in
      connection with business transactions. Data may be transferred across borders where legally
      permitted and protected with appropriate safeguards.
  </p>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>
      Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or restrict
      processing of your Personal Information, and to withdraw consent where applicable.
  </p>

  <h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
  <p>
      Services are not directed to children under 14. If personal data from a minor is identified, it
      will be handled and removed as required by law.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
      For privacy requests, contact EXIT Realty Corp. International:
      2626 Argentia Road, Mississauga, Ontario, L5N 5N2, Canada · Phone: 905-363-4050 ·
      Email: exit@exitrealty.com
  </p>
